# Sprint 1 Final — Data Inventory (v5.1)

**59 features | OBS_DIM = 118 | OBS_SCHEMA_VERSION = 5**

## Schema Diff from v4 → v5.1

```diff
Features: 38 → 59 (+21 net)
OBS_DIM: 76 → 118
Added: 22 new features
Removed: 1 (taker_buy_ratio_5s — algebraically redundant)
Fixed: OI delta clamp ±1.0 → ±20.0%
```

