### I) Open Interest (slots 54–58)

> Semantic: **oi_delta_* values are percentage changes** (e.g., `5.0 = 5% increase`).
> Clamped at **±20%** to cover normal variation and extreme liquidation cascades.

| Slot | Feature | Formula | Unit | Window | Clamp | Invalidation |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| 54 | `oi_value` | from exchange | USD | instant | raw | `None` if never received |
| 55 | **`oi_delta_30s`** ★ | [(OI[t]-OI[t-30s])/OI[t-30s]*100](file:///C:/Bot%20mk3/crates/bot-server/src/services/orchestrator/risk.rs#314-318) | **% change** | 30s, min_age 25s | **±20.0** | `None` if no OI ≥25s old |
| 56 | **`oi_delta_1m`** ★ | same formula | **% change** | 60s, min_age 50s | **±20.0** | `None` if no OI ≥50s old |
| 57 | `oi_delta_5m` | same formula | **% change** | 5m, min_age 4.5m | **±20.0** | `None` if no OI ≥4.5m old |
| 58 | `oi_zscore_30m` | [(OI-μ)/σ](file:///C:/Bot%20mk3/crates/bot-server/src/services/orchestrator/risk.rs#314-318) | z-score | 30-min EWMA | ±10.0 | `None` until EWMA ready |

